{"type": "article", "id": 32767, "title": "抖森为Gucci拍大片，以及，来看10个 2017 春夏流行色 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-29T02:59:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4380, "name": "Pantone"}, {"id": 7350, "name": "瑞士手表"}, {"id": 8841, "name": "美国大选"}, {"id": 33307, "name": "2017春夏流行色"}, {"id": 357, "name": "沃尔玛"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 20739, "name": "STUSSY"}, {"id": 25746, "name": "Ivy Park"}, {"id": 28973, "name": "Topman"}, {"id": 33308, "name": "bagjack"}, {"id": 3814, "name": "Beyonce"}, {"id": 33309, "name": "Tom Hiddleston"}, {"id": 33310, "name": "Trump"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160929095413FntiPG0vTEAIe16K.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/wal-mart-in-talks-to-invest-up-to-1-billion-in-indias-flipkart\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>沃尔玛或将向印度的 Flipkart 投资 10 亿美元</b></a> | Flipkart 是印度最大的电商，它最近的估值为 160 亿美元。此前， Amazon 也有意投资 Flipkart。目前沃尔玛和 Flipkart 的交易还在洽谈中。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/sears-claires-at-high-risk-in-fitch-study-of-retail-failures\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国多个零售商正在面临一年内违约的高风险</b></a> | 据 Fitch Ratings 的研究称，由于在提升网购服务上的巨大投入，美国多个零售商正在面临着一年内违约欠款的高风险。其中包括美国最大的私人零售商 Sears 百货，Claire’s 饰品公司以及 Nine West 集团。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/lvmhs-digital-drive-takes-time-despite-apple-hire\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团的数字化进程进展缓慢</b></a> | 一年前，LVMH 雇佣了前 Apple Music 的执行官 Ian Rogers 来发展集团的数字化策略。不过，这个拥有超过 70 个事业品牌的奢侈品集团目前的数字化进程进展仍然缓慢，大大低于投资者的预期。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/swiss-watchmakers-expect-negative-future-outlook/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>瑞士手表制造商的未来发展不被看好</b></a> | 据德勤咨询的数据表明，瑞士手表的出口额在 2016 年前八个月下降了 10.9%，其中，香港市场作为瑞士手表重要的出口市场，下降了 27.6%。香港市场的衰落，美国和印度成为了瑞士手表的下一个最具潜力的市场。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/topshoptopman-open-first-german-stores-in-berlin-and-oberhausen-in-november-10568813/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Topshop 兄弟品牌 Topman 入驻德国</b></a> | Topman 计划在 10 月 17 日，在德国柏林开设首家店铺。接下来的一周之后，在奥伯豪森开设第二家店。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">美国大选进行白热化，设计公司也推出了<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/donald-trump-pins\" rel=\"nofollow\">恶搞 Trump 的徽章</a>。通过把「Don’t be a sucker」、「Don’t Trump」、「Dump Trump」等犀利言语设计成卡通图案，表达对 Trump 的讽刺。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090524gtnamQ7qKC9Xw0Ai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290905247zpQGPgR31LcAn0S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090524kd2XqaWFnzQDc86C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090525DIo2CGTwpMBZsal3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090525WbHVCX9QK25Gdwu8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090525cC6kAEKqhrxev2mQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290905395mJ2eVxonbYpfcTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090539dv50QwHhOqiSjgNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090539gT6CDbI2dPR5fums.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090545LEhNQtH3ATcpRg1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>抖森 Tom Hiddleston 成了 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/tom-hiddleston-is-the-new-face-of-gucci/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 2017</a> 的广告主角，广告片中 Tom 的英伦绅士魅力尽显。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090619CXsVzoSGmlnOJg9x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.914063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290906053lMV4OSkczTE7YLW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.914063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090604bhOWPlNxHsEB5t27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.914516\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090605A9mbUOQq7GLT3ane.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Beyoncé 的个人品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/beyonce-ivy-park-2016-fall-winter-first-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ivy Park 发布 2016 秋冬新作</a>。该系列延续了运动与时尚相结合的风格，以 Ivy Park 的 logo 贯穿其中，还带来了大衣、连帽衫与圆领卫衣等秋冬季的保暖单品。售价从 25 到 200 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090700seiEcMBza5KRnl6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090700dgw8nWBJ2UbiCOkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090700xc4C1l6XQhwVByaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090700W2Dgf78nqXPr5ypa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.492000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092909070080PI7S1yimLuaB6k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290907006LkzGI1o2xFBtmyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090717HzEgQpvNnhaPURqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/stussy-livin-general-store-bagjack-backpack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stüssy 与德国制包品牌 bagjack  合作</a>，推出了 2016 秋冬全新系列。该系列由 bagjack 的创始人 Peter Brunsberg 亲自设计，沿用德国标准，手工工艺制作。售价为 38000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090728V8LaWnH2zSwbBGPF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290907483b7SzKFnokEJWXrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290907481SCRqcxbNTXdDYKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090748MgWjR6mzISF109l3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090748bOhvcY5mf21UQlMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Pantone 公布的 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/trends-fashion/pantone-fashion-color-report-spring-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 春夏流行色</a>，除了尼加拉之外，还有其他九个选择。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090801VolcBs0DZ5FEXubR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090820dtY21EgXbQ9N7pqs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092909082051LSlIuPQeWUDoY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090821Wldgy2OZ45rnhQpu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090821syAJ8dTQcbP4gYLn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090821wcbrA9VLemz5JSvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090820QGavxKjSU6Rqg1ue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092909083480MYBa3hzKUHFefW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090834Ay3KD0pO5eBiI1tR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090834zqiAld2RfNGcMP0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/mango-takes-road-trip-october-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mango 的十月宣传大片</a>，以公路旅行为主题展现 80 年代的复古风。取景地为洛杉矶，并请来了模特 Grace Hartzel 与 Shelby Hayes 共同出镜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090846d9T2ZPA7KYqIjhrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290908462Qhdz8TuZGS6o4ny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609290908476bKIdCvy7qYSouED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090847FoP5IBu6AaUVQv8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090847M5iyKpFhcL8bgxkj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090846VpUw0kFbo6ML8QsE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160929090853RHcfUCwjoEqlMnYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}